 eNCA's wekeend breakfast show 'Weekend Wake Up' focused on young authors for its book club segment this week.Author of 'How Many Ways Can You Say Hello' Refiloe Moahloli, was in studio to discuss this week's books.She started by explaining what inspired her book, and then discussed the other books of the week.How Many Ways Can You Say Hello was published in February this year and is available at Exclusive Books.eNCA